CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 20, 1971, pg. 17 reads: "Mrs. Gwen Jeter is a homemake and mother. She is the wife of Bobby Jeter of the Green Bay Packers Pre-Football team.  They reside in Wilkinsburg. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Gwen Jeter wearing light colored gown with one shoulder, and dark elbow length gloves, posed in front of floral curtains with tassels
